// Key Concepts:
// Swagger - API documentation & testing tool (auto-generates UI from code)
// Swashbuckle - NuGet package to integrate Swagger with ASP.NET Core
// ProducesResponseType - Documents expected HTTP status codes in Swagger
// Postman - API testing tool to send HTTP requests manually
// Route attribute - Customizes URL pattern (e.g. [Route("api/emp")])